window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><i>The dragon chooses you.</i></p> <p>I thought I knew what a bad day was. Then I woke up in chains, trapped inside a tower with a dragon egg in my lap and a handsome assassin out for my blood.</p> <p>I've been transported to a magical world, responsible for a newborn baby dragon and being chased by everyone in the empire. I’m the next Dragon Seeker, a guide bound to serve the realm’s most powerful ruler. If I don’t survive this enchanted world, my dragon, Ametine, will fall to peril, and the kingdom will be plunged into chaos at the hands of an evil king.</p> <p>I wish I could focus on saving the world, but it’s hard to do when I'm on the run… and the assassin hunting me is the sexiest guy I've ever met.</p> <p>But I’ve got news for the evil king. He wants my dragon?</p> <p>I'll end his rule first.</p> <p>Dragon Seeker<i> is a hilarious, action-packed, and slightly-spicy romantasy novella full of adventure, magical realms, and witty banter. Suitable for ages 18+</i></p>"; 
